u1ec7u n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd AI (TOPS):", "value": "L\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 50 TOPS"}, {"label": "Card m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh:", "value": "Card t\u00edch h\u1ee3p - AMD Radeon Graphics"}, {"label": "RAM:", "value": "24 GB"}, {"label": "Lo\u1ea1i RAM:", "value": "LPDDR5X (Onboard)"}, {"label": "T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 Bus RAM:", "value": "8000 MHz"}, {"label": "H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 RAM t\u1ed1i \u0111a:", "value": "Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p"}, {"label": "K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh:", "value": "16\""}, {"label": "\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i:", "value": "2.8K (2880 x 1800) - OLED 16:10"}, {"label": "T\u1ea5m n\u1ec1n:", "value": "OLED"}, {"label": "\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u1ee7 m\u00e0u:", "value": "100% DCI-P3"}, {"label": "C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh:", "value": "1.07 t\u1ef7 m\u00e0u"}, {"label": "C\u1ed5ng giao ti\u1ebfp:", "value": "1 x USB Type-C 3.2 (h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Power Delivery v\u00e0 DisplayPort)"}, {"label": "K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y:", "value": "Bluetooth 5.3"}, {"label": "\u0110\u00e8n b\u00e0n ph\u00edm:", "value": "\u0110\u00e8n chuy\u1ec3n m\u00e0u RGB - 1 v\u00f9ng"}, {"label": "B\u1ea3o m\u1eadt:", "value": "Nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t (FaceID)"}, {"label": "T\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t:", "value": "H\u00e3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1"}, {"label": "Th\u00f4ng tin Pin:", "value": "4-cell Li-ion, 75 Wh"}, {"label": "H\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh:", "value": "Windows 11 Home SL + Office Home 2024 v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n + Microsoft 365 Basic"}, {"label": "Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ra m\u1eaft:", "value": "2025"}, {"label": "K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc:", "value": "D\u00e0i 353.6 mm - R\u1ed9ng 246.9 mm - D\u00e0y 15.9 mm - 1.5 kg"}]', '[{"content": "C\u00e2u hinh tam \u00f4n cho doanh nh\u00e2n doanh nghi\u00eap v\u01b0a va nho.Ram chi h\u00f4 tr\u01a1 t\u00f4i \u0111a 24GB. Man hinh si\u00eau \u0111ep si\u00eau net, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u0103p may mau \u0111en r\u00e2t d\u00ea bi bam m\u00f4 h\u00f4i tay , cham nhe cung dinh, phai lau li\u00ean tuc n\u00eau kh\u00f4ng mu\u00f4n may sach \u0111ep.C\u0103m sac khi dung se bi gi\u01b0t nhe, b\u00ean DMX co \u0111\u00f4i cho minh 1 may khac nh\u01b0ng cung v\u00e2n bi. Co le do vo kim loai n\u00ean ko tranh khoi \u0111i\u00eau nay. Khi g\u00e2p man hinh lai thi ban l\u00ea ko kh\u01a1p hoan toan, m\u00f4t b\u00ean cao b\u00ean th\u00e2p khi \u0111\u00ea may ng\u01b0a l\u00ean, th\u00e2m chi h\u01a1 n\u00eau ko bop manh. Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean giai thich \u0111i\u00eau nay la binh th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean th\u00f4i minh cung ch\u00e2p nh\u00e2n, \u0111\u00f4i tra hoai cung m\u00eat.Ban nh\u00e2n Vi\u00ean t\u00ean Lu\u00e2n \u01a1 DMX L\u00ea V\u0103n Kh\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00eat tinh \u0111\u00f4i tra va h\u00f4 tr\u01a1 cho khach.N\u00eau may co th\u00eam option mau bac n\u01b0a thi OK.", "rating": 5, "date": "2026-02-12T07:59:19.054000"}]', '[-0.06884765625, -0.035888671875, -0.007049560546875, -0.06640625, 0.0303955078125, 0.0224609375, 0.0380859375, 0.0322265625, -0.0703125, -0.009765625, -0.03369140625, 0.032958984375, 0.04052734375, -0.0076904296875, -0.037353515625, 0.004119873046875, 0.02392578125, 0.0732421875, -0.024658203125, 0.09765625, -0.02783203125, 0.0093994140625, -0.0216064453125, 0.07080078125, 0.0018310546875, 0.0040283203125, -0.040771484375, 0.047119140625, 0.00958251953125, 0.01129150390625, -0.017333984375, 0.0283203125, 0.006500244140625, -0.00787353515625, 0.0245361328125, -0.00921630859375, 0.00095367431640625, 0.042724609375, -0.0228271484375, 0.056884765625, 0.05322265625, 0.014892578125, -0.045166015625, 0.005035400390625, -0.0206298828125, -0.038330078125, -0.0299072265625, 0.032470703125, 0.036865234375, -0.0031585693359375, -0.0145263671875, 0.0045166015625, 0.0021514892578125, -0.0255126953125, -0.0361328125, -0.00041961669921875, 0.0101318359375, -0.0125732421875, 0.00665283203125, -0.003143310546875, -0.0238037109375, 0.0859375, 0.0032806396484375, 0.01458740234375, 0.01385498046875