lue": "6 GB"}, {"label": "Dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u tr\u1eef:", "value": "128 GB"}, {"label": "Dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i (kh\u1ea3 d\u1ee5ng) kho\u1ea3ng:", "value": "109.4 GB"}, {"label": "Th\u1ebb nh\u1edb:", "value": "MicroSD, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 1.5 TB"}, {"label": "Danh b\u1ea1:", "value": "Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n"}, {"label": "Ch\u00ednh 50 MP & Ph\u1ee5 2 MP", "value": "Ch\u00ednh 50 MP & Ph\u1ee5 2 MP"}, {"label": "8 MP", "value": "8 MP"}, {"label": "T\u00ednh n\u0103ng camera tr\u01b0\u1edbc:", "value": "B\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc m\u00e0u"}, {"label": "M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh r\u1ed9ng:", "value": "6.7\" - T\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 qu\u00e9t 90 Hz"}, {"label": "480 nits", "value": "480 nits"}, {"label": "Dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng pin:", "value": "5000 mAh"}, {"label": "H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 s\u1ea1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a:", "value": "25 W"}, {"label": "Ghi \u00e2m:", "value": "Ghi \u00e2m cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi"}, {"label": "Radio:", "value": "C\u00f3"}, {"label": "Xem phim:", "value": "3G2"}, {"label": "Nghe nh\u1ea1c:", "value": "3GA"}, {"label": "Jack tai nghe:", "value": "3.5 mm"}, {"label": "Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u:", "value": "Khung & M\u1eb7t l\u01b0ng nh\u1ef1a"}, {"label": "K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:", "value": "D\u00e0i 167.3 mm - Ngang 77.3 mm - D\u00e0y 8 mm - N\u1eb7ng 191 g"}, {"label": "Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ra m\u1eaft:", "value": "03/2025"}, {"label": "H\u00e3ng:", "value": "Samsung. Xem th\u00f4ng tin h\u00e3ng"}]', '[{"content": "Samsung A06 5G b\u1ea3n 6Gb/128Gb n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng mua nh\u00e9.M\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00ean c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1ch quan. Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean TGDD nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, h\u00e0ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.M\u00e1y d\u00f9ng ch\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m m\u00e1y ph, mua t\u1eb7ng ph\u1ee5 huynh \u00f4ng b\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0m m\u00e1y ch\u00ednh th\u00ec l\u1ea5n c\u1ea5n v\u1ee5 NFC. M\u1edbi mua v\u1ec1 h\u01a1i lag n\u00ean v\u00e0o c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u00ean One UI 8, Android 16, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt xong sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t g\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i x\u00f3a m\u1ea5y app kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft t\u1eaft + bu\u1ed9c d\u1eebng m\u1ea5y app \u00edt s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00e2ng cao h\u01a1n th\u00ec d\u00f9ng ADB x\u00f3a app r\u00e1c c\u00e1i n\u00e0y chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u1eaft c\u0169ng ok r\u1ed3i m\u00e1y s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e0i app c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0o v.vM\u00e1y ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng SSVN c\u00f3 5G r\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i VN, m\u00ecnh mua gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 2tr83tr do app m\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 TGDD ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3, mua t\u1ea1i c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u00f3 m\u00e3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh m\u00e1y ngang li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u00f4 l\u00ean nh\u01b0 h\u00e3ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c cao c\u1ea5p, vu\u1ed1t ch\u1ea1m c\u0169ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i m\u00e0n ngang v\u1edbi vi\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u00e1y cao c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi c\u00f3, c\u1ea7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n do ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p.M\u00e1y nghe g\u1ecdi l\u01b0\u1edbt web d\u00f9ng app r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n, s\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5G ngon, Chip c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t trong ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng t\u1ea7m gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n G99, Wifi 5, Bluetooth 5.3, kh\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ee5i IP54. ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 NFC v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh m\u00e0 m\u00e0n l\u00ean kho\u1ea3ng FHD th\u00ec th\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea5m v\u1ee1 m\u1ed3m c\u00e1c m\u00e1y n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Trung v\u00e0 h\u00e3ng kh\u00e1c.Mua \u1edf TGDD y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1eadu m\u00e3i. C\u00e1i h\u1eadu m\u00e3i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9.", "rating": 5, "date": "2026-02-12T07:59:19.058000"}, {"content": "M\u00ecnh m\u1edbi mua \u0111x 2 th\u00e1g m\u00e0 h\u01b0 d\u00e2y s\u1ea1c c\u00f3 b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh hok \u1ea1", "rating": 5, "date": "2026-02-12T07:59:19.058000"}]', '[-0.047607421875, 0.0140380859375, -0.00457763671875, -0.07568359375, 0.052978515625, -0.013916015625, 0.03759765625, 0.031494140625, -0.0230712890625, -0.04150390625, -0.0400390625, 0.0262451171875, -0.0174560546875, -0.005126953125, -0.0390625, -0.010986328125, 0.05908203125, 0.038330078125, 0.00347900390625, 0.1181640625, -0.06298828125, 0.046142578125, -0.0267333984375, 0.037109375, 0.0634765625, 0.00604248046875, -0.03125, -0.00921630859375, 0.006805419921875, 0.042236328125, 0.0185546875, 0.0380859375, -0.041259765625, -0.014404296875, -0.0184326171875, -0.006317138671875, 0.03271484375, 0.01904296875, 0.0279541015625, 0.0238037109375, 0.01495361328125, -0.026123046875, -0.0308837890625, -0.019775390625, -0.041259765625, -0.0184326171875, 0.0015106201171875, -0.021484375, 0.023681640625, 0.001983642578125, 0.04150390625, -0.01361083984375, 0.04931640625, -0.030029296875, 0.0250244140625, 0.0306396484375, 0.00445556640625, -0.0016937255859375, 0.031494140625, -0.00592041015625, -0.07080078125, 0.046142578125, 0.0103759765625, 0.06591796875, -0.0086669921875, 0.0174560546875, 0.004364013671875, 0.0068359375, 0.01177978515625, 0.000438690185546875, -0.006805419921875, -0.0224609375, 0.00946044921875, 0.01300048828125, -0.000888824462890625, 0.035888671875, 0.0126953125, -0.007568359375, 0.010009765625, -0.00836181640625, 0.0023345947265625, 0.078125, 0.0155029296875, -0.06396484375, -0.0240478515625, 0.0284423828125, 0.0189208984375, -0.01611328125, -0.0281982421875, -0.01019287109375, 0.0390625, 0.0162353515625, -0.03369140625, -0.00970458984375, -6.437301635742188e-05, 0.058349609375, 0.0162353515625, -0.032470703125, -0.02734375, -0.02111